  1001::1:80/TCP => 2001::1:8080/TCP (test/backend1, active)
  1001::1:443/TCP => 2001::1:8443/TCP (test/backend1, active)
  1001::1:443/UDP => 2001::1:8443/UDP (test/backend1, active), 2001::2:8443/UDP (test/backend2, active)
